{"tid":164251,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一星期得 $500 生活費，第時家用比幾多好","createTime":"2017-03-20T14:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T07:00:43.000Z","uid":14170,"like":15,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37f652a8245bc54763bd7a4d6b13dc19f0d717d0","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150513355822c7910d861dd4aa92fadcdb7f39d8","tid":164251,"uid":4599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"你幾大？"},{"pid":"6f46aa39426ded267d728bcff219354c8e700d2d","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:15:16.000Z","msg":"中學個陣一個月得 $250 (五餐)生活費，無交通費因爲間學校 35 分鐘步程 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搞到無錢同同學出街，慢慢就無咩熟既朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直都好嬲屋企人點解有錢都肯唔比多少少我"},{"pid":"0e0dba5ea9248088be1445873e86d7745ee0b8ad","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級"},{"pid":"52464bda657814f9995666dbe98ebeb81e854551","tid":164251,"uid":10680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e87cc68c55d41d5241645c9a103fc5f6f73752ad","tid":164251,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:18:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母過左18歲重要問屋企拎錢<br />\n廢人"},{"pid":"22545bbf12ee650d8c624e1585a40f6abbaacd8b","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級</blockquote><br />\n依家一直都有返 PT，之前自己出錢去左兩個 Exchange 洗左成十萬，依家無錢剩了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好羨慕啲人屋企有錢比個仔周圍去見識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178668fcdcd82b6b4d317d8a86f3b61bed2faf99","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母過左18歲重要問屋企拎錢<br />\n廢人</blockquote><br />\n大佬讀書唔洗時間咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c9431ec1c8fa652ee3cf4869bf6d1e83ce4e37","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母過左18歲重要問屋企拎錢<br />\n廢人</blockquote><br />\n大佬讀書唔洗時間咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係話要屋企養，而係屋企有錢點解唔可以養住我先，比我專心讀書 / 學多樣語言都好呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：之前兩年瘋狂返工無拎家用，依家返 pt intern 拎緊最低工資 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以先要拎返家用"},{"pid":"65619071999b4fbc19c1552c15411ddc61e79e05","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"啲 pt intern 時間長，人工少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay off 返足一日八個鐘，人工同我補兩個鐘習一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哂我時間又搵唔到錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先至逼住用老母錢，佢都唔想比我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d30a3ffd10e5deaab1265dae88dbb492bd47b10","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:25:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母過左18歲重要問屋企拎錢<br />\n廢人</blockquote><br />\n大佬讀書唔洗時間咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大佬咁多 test midterm lab assignment <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係求合格個班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9705adb4e491ec8a21e75600432ab6025500a0dc","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"唉好辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad8be2b4f845e8b2f2a83e3412daae230c8225a","tid":164251,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"一星期500你都用到叫曬春，我一個月1000叫咩？"},{"pid":"e1e20e68e0bdb2412367abfed74703d24fd58c4b","tid":164251,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母過左18歲重要問屋企拎錢<br />\n廢人</blockquote><br />\n大佬讀書唔洗時間咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大佬咁多 test midterm lab assignment <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係求合格個班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你咪補多幾個鐘習囉 廢人 <br />\n好撚威咩 唔係求合格 拎乜grade 咁把閉 咁大個人仲要用個grade黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf946446eb416d8c19d99e26ca6a2d858011d47a","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母過左18歲重要問屋企拎錢<br />\n廢人</blockquote><b