/blockquote><br />\n自費去左兩個 exchange <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無人叫你去 同埋除左pt 都好多方法搵錢 <br />\nA- 姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  連分配時間都唔識？ <br />\nFirst hon 咪又係咁拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6cef7e6b2e540328f0963afbdc6a6285ec7fde5","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你幾大？</blockquote><br />\n大學三年級</blockquote><br />\n屌你老母過左18歲重要問屋企拎錢<br />\n廢人</blockquote><br />\n大佬讀書唔洗時間咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大佬咁多 test midterm lab assignment <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係求合格個班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你咪補多幾個鐘習囉 廢人 <br />\n好撚威咩 唔係求合格 拎乜grade 咁把閉 咁大個人仲要用個grade黎打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平均 A- <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無打打飛機，只係講讀書都要時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解你講到講大學 = 瘋狂返工<br />\n作為學生我想學野，唔係返工，工以後我有幾十年返<br />\n唔明點解有得學野唔學都要去返工，屋企又唔係無錢開飯"},{"pid":"e2e7f1b700d6fa35f292edb775ca8a1e956b073f","tid":164251,"uid":7030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"咁都唔夠 你平時食咩？<br />\n又唔係要你交埋水費電費煤氣費"},{"pid":"e144d10f078de8249e3b4d2a9ecc105ede4c5d65","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>補咁多ive仔都唔夠錢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自費去左兩個 exchange <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkg