sg":"以前會怨佢地比得少<br />\n但開始返Parttime知做野辛苦 <br />\n都唔好意思問佢地攞零用啦 辛苦錢黎架<br />\n自己賺自己洗先心安理得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298ac752091dbc0283771425429a21ff7dd9f6e0","tid":164251,"uid":30333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:01:18.000Z","msg":"以前問老豆老母攞親零用錢都要俾佢地屌一大輪 而家返工個個月俾家用係以前零用嘅兩倍幾三倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67198a2f2f5cfb49624a6690aca21866294fed1b","tid":164251,"uid":37067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:18:46.000Z","msg":"班友唔抵得姐<br />\n公平架<br />\n佢地比幾多你 第日咪比返幾多囉<br />\n食多幾年大學第時咪比多少少家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34407576e6685df41dd9d70e53dda131dbfc3663","tid":164251,"uid":92643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"我出黎打工,一個月都係得2000左右駛用,其餘用晒係屋企<br />\n<br />\n利申:以前中五以後所有學費同駛用自己搵,至於第時比幾錢家用你可以唔比架,唔駛係到問咁大個人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e829d832b7fd4d996fffbf015ebb08d5c1388e","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個叫你淨係做intern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔夠咪炒散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左18平時又有返工 點解仲要俾生活費你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就唔信你會多野做到冇時間打機出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲科唔返intern 唔比你pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知樓主個個係咪<br />\n<br />\n唔好講到18就一定要出黎做野啦<br />\n出黎做pt可以搵到幾多姐<br />\n返學搭車食飯唔洗錢嘅？<br />\n唔夠用想問屋企拎下都比人屌<br />\n身邊大把朋友都唔洗返pt 屋企比生活費</blockquote><br />\n我屋企都叫有小小錢 讀緊要返intern 既科<br />\n做pt搵得唔多架 不過夠我得閒買下衫食下自助餐sem break 去下旅行咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返學搭車食飯都自己俾<br />\n有手有腳有返工仲攤大手問老豆老母拎錢會唔會醜左小小 無錢唔好去玩 玩完要自己承擔後果<br />\n身邊有朋友唔洗返pt 屋企比生活費不過唔會好笑到要屋企人俾錢佢去玩同學野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我更多朋友係自己努力返工 甚至養埋細佬妹</blockquote><br />\n返到幾多工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家返 pt intern，用呢份 intern 既經驗再報 Summer intern，咁我畢業就有 1st hon 加三個比賽獎項，兩個 exchange 兩份 intern <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我做呢啲都係想把握機會增值自己，無論將來工作定讀書都有個好睇既 CV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我只係想問點解屋企人唔肯幫我，唔肯比資源我更上一層姐"},{"pid":"e137f7d8ba7459914b694ca6fd86e72d95d2b942","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有錢又要用哂去exchange<br />\n然後話自已冇錢用怨屋企人<br />\non99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁有 GPA 又報到唔通放棄機會咩<br />\n<br />\n日本政府比左獎學金 32 萬 YEN"},{"pid":"30daa3996044de57f9a09a0d62c9ca95841ee156","tid":164251,"uid":31,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"35分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解唔搭車"},{"pid":"cb6c2c3fe6001abace13a06895426af3fa434a50","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鏗哥exchange hku比幾多船</blockquote><br />\n一萬，不過我 rej 左<br />\n<br />\n因為日本個邊比左二萬幾我，遲早 HKU 都要回收返個筆錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6daf166d5ce56f8d6e99a3f6d47b5a257117e4eb","tid":164251,"uid":5459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:30:48.000Z","msg":"人地屋企畀得起，成班憤青屌人做乜？人地屋企窮仲攤大手板拎就話啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"386c92502361c54caead60e42a7c8fa57c1f3425","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"