 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n窮人就咪撚生啦 自己就懶唔做野 搞到屋企好窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲旨意個女一畢業就搵到份好工養你兩件蛀米大蟲加多個讀緊書ge屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連男朋友同我傾第時d野 我都覺得前路茫茫 一份糧養4個人 仲想草錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n生你既目的就係為左要比你養 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4246968000fa8a3ab3ac1326d04e6a1c48ff332a","tid":164251,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T16:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由yr1開始就無零用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個陣都無，係依家返左份 pt intern + 搵唔多補習先問佢拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d3fb0f21cb5ada0bf7484ce20278db4dfba02c","tid":164251,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T20:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊個叫你淨係做intern<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔夠咪炒散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左18平時又有返工 點解仲要俾生活費你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就唔信你會多野做到冇時間打機出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲科唔返intern 唔比你pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知樓主個個係咪<br />\n<br />\n唔好講到18就一定要出黎做野啦<br />\n出黎做pt可以搵到幾多姐<br />\n返學搭車食飯唔洗錢嘅？<br />\n唔夠用想問屋企拎下都比人屌<br />\n身邊大把朋友都唔洗返pt 屋企比生活費</blockquote><br />\n我屋企都叫有小小錢 讀緊要返intern 既科<br />\n做pt搵得唔多架 不過夠我得閒買下衫食下自助餐sem break 去下旅行咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返學搭車食飯都自己俾<br />\n有手有腳有返工仲攤大手問老豆老母拎錢會唔會醜左小小 無錢唔好去玩 玩完要自己承擔後果<br />\n身邊有朋友唔洗返pt 屋企比生活費不過唔會好笑到要屋企人俾錢佢去玩同學野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我更多朋友係自己努力返工 甚至養埋細佬妹</blockquote><br />\n返到幾多工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家返 pt intern，用呢份 intern 既經驗再報 Summer intern，咁我畢業就有 1st hon 加三個比賽獎項，兩個 exchange 兩份 intern <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我做呢啲都係想把握機會增值自己，無論將來工作定讀書都有個好睇既 CV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我只係想問點解屋企人唔肯幫我，唔肯比資源我更上一層姐</blockquote><br />\n嘩好叻叻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都係想我咁講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當你intern最低工資一個月一千 屋企俾2000你<br />\n3000都唔夠一個月洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話自己要讀書要2個intern 咁忙返唔到工好辛苦又可以去學野增值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小心咁忙冇時間溫書變2nd up 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3f7eb0c44736c26339ce4caecc01a14d194288","tid":164251,"uid":70192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T23:53:47.000Z","msg":"起碼6000"},{"pid":"1cf5d42cd837b86c24c74d5d5ef1379fc789b623","tid":164251,"uid":49928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:25:01.000Z","msg":"同樓主差唔多 <br />\n不過係每日得50蚊 <br />\n車錢冇左20蚊 <br />\n食飯budget 係30蚊 超過要自己補貼 <br />\n我都好唔想靠屋企 <br />\n但無耐自己廢 學業 番工 拍拖 好難balance <br />\n加上又final year 忍唔住quit左份pt <br />\n好想畢業前可以儲到幾萬蚊做下投資 但無望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77855a1a2e930566e8d2c970aeed4132fadeec12","tid":164251,"uid":87988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"讀中學個陣無生活費<br />\n大學個陣自己賺自己洗<br />\n咪又係咁生存 不過無生活姐"}]}